@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #84219 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
P-medium seems ok - I would say P-low for requiring -Coverflow-checks, except that I think it might still be buggy without the checks and just fail silently
It might hide an actual bug, which is why I'm slightly concerned.
well this can only happen if at least one error occurs, so I don't think this needs to be higher than p-medium
